entries.femaleVariant: Yeah, but less than they said they would. What can you do? No negotiating with major players.
Tell the rest not to take gigs from 'em, then. They'll learn to keep their promises real quick.
Nah, they'll always find someone. If not us, some gang.
Tell some 6th Street flag-waver that you're workin' for the NUSA, that gonk'll do it pro bono.
Ugh, like I always say. Idealists're ruinin' the biz.
Mhm, sure are. Least they die off quick.
